    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，中国计划发行 2840 亿美元主权债券以提振经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-plans-284-billion-sovereign-debt-to-lift-economy-reuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，中国计划今年发行 2 万亿元人民币（2844.3 亿美元）的特别主权债券，政策制定者正推出紧急刺激计划，以重振世界第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-plans-284-billion-sovereign-debt-to-lift-economy-reuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《先锋报》称，中国刺激计划只是“众多举措中的第一步”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-needs-to-adopt-elements-of-global-financial-crisis-playbook-vanguard-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“货币政策将在某种程度上无效。财政政策，我们需要更多，”先锋集团首席经济学家乔·戴维斯在彭博电视台讨论中国为支撑经济所做的努力时表示。“无论他们是否愿意承认，中国官员在 2010-2011 年期间都必须采用一些西方策略，”戴维斯在谈到应对全球金融危机时补充道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/china-needs-to-adopt-elements-of-global-financial-crisis-playbook-vanguard-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产将以 5.51 亿美元回购雷诺重组股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nissan-to-buy-back-551-million-in-shares-in-renault-realignment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司将从雷诺汽车公司回购价值 799 亿日元（5.51 亿美元）的股份，这是重新平衡与这家法国汽车制造商的联盟协议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nissan-to-buy-back-551-million-in-shares-in-renault-realignment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿业短缺导致阿达尼价值数十亿美元的铜矿开采放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/adani-s-billion-dollar-copper-play-slows-amid-mining-shortfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球矿石短缺限制了加工企业的供应，高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 投资 12 亿美元的铜冶炼厂将面临缓慢的增长速度，无法达到其额定产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/adani-s-billion-dollar-copper-play-slows-amid-mining-shortfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:33:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行与财政部、瑞士金融市场监管局合作制定银行抵押品规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/snb-working-on-bank-collateral-rules-with-finance-ministry-finma</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行正在与政府及金融监管机构 Finma 合作制定规则，允许该国所有银行以抵押品的形式从央行提取紧急流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/snb-working-on-bank-collateral-rules-with-finance-ministry-finma</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:33:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注数据和美联储发言人，美国国债价格波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/treasuries-drift-as-market-counts-down-to-data-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四晚些时候，美联储将公布一系列数据，并发表讲话，这可能决定美联储是否在 11 月份再次大幅降息，交易员们暂停了美国国债的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/treasuries-drift-as-market-counts-down-to-data-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济承诺出台后，新兴市场面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/emerging-markets-ride-risk-on-wave-after-china-s-economy-pledges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国政府承诺实施新一轮经济刺激政策的推动，新兴市场股市连续第六天上涨，带动风险资产普遍上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/emerging-markets-ride-risk-on-wave-after-china-s-economy-pledges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 09:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
